latestIgtvVideos.title: To us 🇮🇳
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Thank you for making it happen!!! 
Forever grateful ♾ 🇮🇳

latestIgtvVideos.title: 5 places on my bucket list!
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Fun getting more travel inspiration from you guys! 😃 In the earlier video I shared places that I have been to and love, and in this one I’m sharing the 5 places which are on my travel bucket list ✈️

latestIgtvVideos.title: Never forgetting my purpose 🇮🇳
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Sharing glimpses of a school visit in Lucknow to discuss the improvement of nutrition with the school authorities and parents, and share a meal and many conversations with the children! As the hours for the @missuniverse finale approach, I know that whether I win or not, I remain true to the cause of providing better access to healthcare and nutrition for all.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Top 5 favourite travel destinations!
latestIgtvVideos.caption: I’ve had the opportunity to travel a fair bit and here I talk about 5 of my most favourite places ✈️

latestIgtvVideos.title: Fashion Rapid Fire! 🔥
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Answering a bunch of questions about my fashion related choices - let me know if you’re enjoying watching these and getting to know me better! ❤️

latestIgtvVideos.title: 21 Questions!
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Since you guys enjoyed watching me pick between this and that, sharing another quick interview that the team made me do spontaneously! ☺️

latestIgtvVideos.title: Leaving for Atlanta @missuniverse 👑
latestIgtvVideos.caption: New drinking game: take a shot every time we say “excited” 😜 But honestly I’m SO thrilled to be representing India 🇮🇳 It’s an honour and your love and support has ensured that all my nervousness turns into positivity 🤗❤️ Embarking on this journey with happiness and faith in my heart.

latestIgtvVideos.title: What’s in my bag!
latestIgtvVideos.caption: My team caught me super candid on a messy bag day 🙈 but watch anyway to know about all the random things you will find in my bag! 👜 And I guess if you can’t find a medical store when you need something, you can rely on my bag 🤪
